Name: Municipal Council
Description: A Governing Body that is accountable for managing the Municipal Corporation.

Name: Humane Society
Description: An Agency, Board or Commission of the Municipality that has as its mission the protection of animals.

Name: City Clerk's Department
Description: A Department of the City that has as its mission the support to the Municipal Council.

Name: Airport Authority
Description: An Agency, Board or Commission of the Municipality that has as its mission the protection of animals.

Name: City Manager's Office
Description: An office of the City that has as its mission to deliver Programs and Services in an optimal manner.

Name: Police Department
Description: A Department of the City that has as its mission the safety from crime.

Name: Fire Department
Description: A Department of the City that has as its mission the safety from life or property threatening incidents.

Name: Asset Management and Public Works Department
Description: A Department of the City that has as its mission the deliver of efficient and effective public works services.

Name: Legal Department
Description: A Department of the City that has as its mission the support to the Corporation in all matters that are legal in nature.

Name: Transit Department
Description: A Department of the City that has as its mission the transport of people by affordable means of mobility.
